items.title: Trump-backed bill to keep US government running fails to pass
items.description: Dozens of Republicans defied Trump and tech billionaire Elon Musk by joining Democrats to reject a revised spending bill.

items.title: Hungary sparks row with Poland by granting asylum to ex-minister
items.description: Marcin Romanowski is facing 11 charges in Poland, including being accused of defrauding the state.

items.title: Child dies in stabbing at Croatian primary school
items.description: The alleged attacker has been arrested, police say.

items.title: Malaysia approves new search for missing flight MH370
items.description: The Boeing 777 carrying 239 people vanished 10 years ago in one of aviation's greatest mysteries.

items.title: Eight migrants drown after boat tries to evade Greek ship
items.description: So far 18 people have been rescued from the sea with many of the survivors suffering from injuries after the incident.
